{"tid":1241475,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥致函全體公務員  承諾繼續帶領政府","createTime":"2019-06-18T17:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T17:21:14.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4c031e12a25a480b6d9f5d9c698a7fd779b7ac0f","tid":1241475,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:09:23.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥晚上致函全體公務員，提到她已就修例引起的矛盾、紛爭及焦慮向公眾致歉，承認特區政府相關工作不足，她個人要為此負上很大責任。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥承認，政府處理修例工作不足，源於她自己低估事情敏感程度，她感謝律政司及保安局人員的付出。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥在信中表示，服務公眾是她終身事業，她承諾繼續帶領政府。她說，今次事件令她體會，作為特首，仍有很多事情要學習，包括要更好平衡不同利益，以及聆聽社會各階層意見。<br />\n<br />\n她又感謝警隊盡忠職守，她對警方及示威者關係緊張，感到難過。她又說，政府總部過去數日要關閉，為在政總上班的公務員帶來不便，她感到抱歉。<br />\n<br />\nCarrie Lam , We want you to stay <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hitc-s.com/i/615/tottenham_fan_holds_up_a_banner_for_arsenal_manager_arsene_wenge_475889.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hitc-s.com%2Fi%2F615%2Ftottenham_fan_holds_up_a_banner_for_arsenal_manager_arsene_wenge_475889.jpg&h=ff1efa38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32f8b80bb219cf9855f4d759d50c7cdd67d648b3","tid":1241475,"uid":62167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:21:14.000Z","msg":"唔洗辭職，反正邊個做都一樣。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收回暴動定性。</span></span>先係重點"}]}